          <span class="nutrition-facts__label">Potassium</span>
          <span class="nutrition-facts__amount">278 mg</span>
          <span class="nutrition-facts__percent">7%</span>
        </div>

        <p class="nutrition-facts__footnote">* DV = Daily Value based on a 2,000 calorie diet</p>
